 "score": 7,
 "justification":Both inputs describe a similar methodology involving a case study with one psychologist and three patients over two weeks.  The only difference is that Input 1 explicitly states the purpose of the case study (to show the effectiveness of a new web platform), while Input 2 does not mention the platform or its purpose.  Therefore, they are nearly identical in terms of methodology but lack one important detail. "" 
}

